cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image captioning using natural language processing, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of Tensor Product Representation (TPR) also involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the evaluation of different models and their performance can be categorized under neural networks (cs.NE).
